  <description><![CDATA[<p>The I Larici is a family-run, chalet-style hotel situated 200m from the heart of <a data-udi="umb://document/632726451b0d4569b6f2cd0d56b628c3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/632726451b0d4569b6f2cd0d56b628c3}" title="Bardonecchia">Bardonecchia</a> with bars and restaurants close by. The Campo Smith ski lifts and ski school are a 10 minute walk away, alternatively the free local bus stops 100m away to quickly whisk you to the three Bardonecchia ski areas. Built in an attractive Alpine style, The I Larici exudes homely comfort. The hotel bar with its open fire has a snug feel and the helpful staff will ensure a friendly welcome. The hotel is made up of a main building and an annexe and bedrooms can be allocated in either building. There is no lift in the annexe so please bear that in mind when booking. </p>]]></description>
